|speakers=4,000,000, second language speakers 8-10 millions (estimation, 2010; the figures by the Ethnologue &lt;ref name=&quot;eth&quot;&gt;{{ethnologue|code=bam}}&lt;/ref&gt; of 2,700,000 are out of date)
|fam1=[[Niger-Congo languages|Niger-Congo]] ?
|fam2=[[Mande languages|Mande]]
|fam3=Western Mande
