===Administrative divisions===


Today, Baku is divided into 11 ''raions'' (administrative districts) and 5 settlements of city type.&lt;ref&gt;{{cite web|url=http://www.bakupages.com/pages/baku/baku_en.php |title=Baku's History |publisher=Bakupages.com |date=2010-03-19 |accessdate=2010-04-17}}&lt;/ref&gt;&lt;ref&gt;{{cite web|url=http://www.kishmish.az/content/Baku_e.html |title=Baku's History |publisher=Kishmish.az |date= |accessdate=2010-04-17}}&lt;/ref&gt; The mayor, presently [[Hajibala Abutalybov]], embodies the executive power of the city.&lt;ref&gt;[http://www.azstat.org/statinfo/demoqraphic/en/010.shtml#s9 Territories, number, density of population and territorial units by economic and administrative regions of Azerbaijan Republic by January 1, 2009]&lt;/ref&gt;

